@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xcvkwp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(v0)
    v0 = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.36 - v2 + 0.89)) + (v2 / wp.abs(v1 + 0.31)))
    tmp = ((v0 - 0.78) - (v2 * 0.71))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.abs((v2 + 0.59 * v0 + 0.62)))
    data[tid] = v0
